data.description: Incredible newly renovated Home on Large corner lot and One-Story LIVING in LEEDS.  Updates Galore: white cabinets, granite counters, stainless appliances including microwave hood, new vinyl plank floors throughout, new windows (2022), new HVAC (2022), new water heater, all new plumbing inside and outside all the way to the sewer main, new electrical and lighting throughout, new insulation.  Open floor plan gives it a huge welcome feeling.  The kitchen is jaw-dropping which includes a large pantry, gorgeous granite countertops, huge island. The split floor plan offers two additional bedrooms, large hall bathroom and a REAL Laundry room.
